		<td width="150" align="left" valign="top" class="row1"><a name="28544"></a><span class="name"><span class="usercolor">Elemer</span></span><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_offline.gif" border="0" align="absbottom" alt="Offline" title="Offline" /><div class="gensmall"><img src="images/ranks/rank_4.gif" alt="Illusionist" title="Illusionist" border="0" /><br />Illusionist</div><div align="left" class="gensmall">Joined:&nbsp;15 Oct 2003</div><div align="left" class="gensmall">Total posts:&nbsp;85</div><div align="left" class="gensmall">Location:&nbsp;Ventura, CA</div><div align="left" class="gensmall">Gender:&nbsp;Male</div></td>
                <td class="row1" width="100%" height="28" valign="top"><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                        <tr>
                                <td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td><a href="viewtopic.php?p=28544&amp;sid=decb47f051d7276546ecdad0d218bfe5#28544"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Fri Mar 05, 2004 5:59 am<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: What is our role??</span></td>
                                <td valign="top" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=28544&amp;sid=decb47f051d7276546ecdad0d218bfe5"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>    </td></tr></table></td>
