<br />
</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
I can't think of another class that has better hastes for their GROUP. Yes, some have self hastes, or pet hastes, but who has the best hastes in the game? If you can find a better haste than an enchanters, that can be cast on a group member, please tell me.
<br />

<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">Quote:
