<br />

<br />
I am not sure what you mean by illusions being nerfed, I have to admit, I have heard this. But, nobody has informed me of what they used to be able to do. So, I guess, I'll have to agree with most of them don't have any real utility. But, they ARE fun <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile.gif" border="0" />)
<br />

<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">Quote:
<br />
