<br />
</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
Usually looking for a Shaman is because their slows are better. They even have disease based slows. It isn't just cause they can live through the agro. I easily live through slow/tash agro. With a combination of runes and the slows I can do this. At lower levels, I learned to not slow as early. And their comment says it is a specialty, that doesn't mean enchanters are the only ones that can do it.
<br />

<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">Quote:
